`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The `IInputProvider` contract has two distinct reset concepts: `postFrame()` clears per-frame accumulators (look deltas, edge-triggered presses), while `dispose()` removes DOM event listeners. Separating these is essential — if you clear listeners in postFrame, mouse look breaks permanently after the first frame.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
