`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
Edge-triggered inputs (jump, interact) use a "pressed this frame" flag set on `keydown` and cleared in `postFrame()`. This means: hold Space for 2 seconds → jump only fires once per frame the key was first pressed, then never again until released + re-pressed. This avoids bunny-hopping from a held Space key while keeping the API simple for the consumer.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
